# Theme

## Typography
- Font: Space Grotesk (Google Fonts)
- Headings: font-weight 600â€“700
- Body: font-weight 400
- Use Tailwind classes: text-gray-100 (primary), text-gray-400 (secondary)

## Colors
- Background: #0F0F0F or #121212
- Text primary: #F4F4F5
- Text secondary: #A1A1AA
- Accents:
  - Red: #FF3C38 (Primary accent) - Used for main CTA buttons, important highlights
  - Yellow: #FFDC00 (Secondary accent) - Used for secondary buttons, links, active states
  - Cyan: #22D3EE (Used sparingly for contrast when needed)

## Color Usage
- Primary Red: Call-to-action buttons, important highlights, pulsing animations
- Secondary Yellow: Navigation active states, secondary buttons, stat values, badges
- Text & UI:
  - White/light gray for primary text
  - Medium gray for secondary text
  - Dark grays for backgrounds and cards

## Layout
- Max width: 1200px, centered
- Horizontal padding: `px-4` (mobile), `px-8` (desktop)
- Section spacing: `py-16`
- Responsive breakpoints: Tailwind (`sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`)
